<item>
            <title>[ZOOKEEPER-570] AsyncHammerTest is broken, callbacks need to validate rc parameter</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/ZOOKEEPER-570</link>
                <project id="12310801" key="ZOOKEEPER">ZooKeeper</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;the asynchammertest is not validating the rc in the callback, more serious is that it is using path in the create callback&lt;br/&gt;
to delete the node, rather than name (which is important in the case of a sequential node creation as in this case)&lt;/p&gt;</description>
