                            <comment id="12774830" author="phunt" created="Sun, 8 Nov 2009 21:50:05 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;same patch as before, however I noticed that there was a serious flaw with the&lt;br/&gt;
verification phase, which restarted the quorum. The restart code was wrong,&lt;br/&gt;
it caused a new quorum to be started, rather than restarting the existing quorum.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This addresses the original cause of the test failing, plus the original patch&apos;s&lt;br/&gt;
fix for the delete not being correct (etc...)&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
